(1333, '_transient_dash_88ae138922fe95674369b1cb3d215a2b', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/12/clifford/''>WordPress 4.4 “Clifford”</a> <span class="rss-date">December 8, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.4 of WordPress, named “Clifford” in honor of jazz trumpeter Clifford Brown, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in 4.4 make your site more connected and responsive. Clifford also introduces a new default theme, Twenty Sixteen. Introducing Twenty Sixteen Our newest default theme, Twenty Sixteen, is a modern take [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wpweekly-episode-219-the-2015-year-in-review-part-2-of-2''>WPTavern: WPWeekly Episode 219 – The 2015 Year in Review Part 2 of 2</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2015/12/the-changing-web/''>Matt: The Changing Web</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/microsoft-adds-wordpress-data-source-and-template-to-windows-app-studio-beta''>WPTavern: Microsoft Adds WordPress Data Source and Template to Windows App Studio Beta</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/updraftplus/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=updraftplus&amp;_wpnonce=a1e180a4a0&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
