(16, 1, '2015-08-20 03:09:31', '2015-08-20 03:09:31', 'The years from 1969 to present saw networked devices balloon from <a href="http://www.walthowe.com/navnet/history.html">four university computers</a> connected via the ARPANET to about two billion humans frequently accessing the Internet today. In the near future that number will exponentially multiply again, from a couple billion networked devices to <a href="http://www.gartner.com/newsroom/id/2684616"><em>tens of billions</em> of embedded processors</a>. Every aspect of our lives will be connected by networked devices: homes, workplaces, vehicles, appliances, tools, toys --you name it.', 'Java: The once and future king of Internet programming', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-20 03:09:31', '2015-08-20 03:09:31', '', 9, 'http://localhost/InnoculateIT/index.php/2015/08/20/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(18, 1, '2015-08-20 03:10:45', '2015-08-20 03:10:45', '', 'speed-light-curves-fast-100568679-primary.idge', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'speed-light-curves-fast-100568679-primary-idge', '', '', '2015-08-20 03:10:45', '2015-08-20 03:10:45', '', 9, 'http://localhost/InnoculateIT/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/speed-light-curves-fast-100568679-primary.idge_.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(20, 1, '2015-08-20 16:38:15', '2015-08-20 16:38:15', '<div class="field field-name-field-description field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">\r\n<div class="field-items">\r\n<div class="field-item even">\r\n\r\nWith the release of Java 8 and planning already underway for Java 9+, the entire 9M+ Java community is energized in learning more about the latest additions to the Java platform and ecosystem. This track will cover new Java features such as Lambdas, Streams, New Concurrency primitives, new JVM languages and explore how to optimize performance in Java-based systems. We''ll also investigate how enterprises are exploring the use of Java Embedded in an Internet of Things world.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="field field-name-field-video field-type-file field-label-hidden"></div>', 'Java Innovations - The Latest Trends in Java Technology', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'java-innovations-the-latest-trends-in-java-technology', '', '', '2015-08-22 18:05:11', '2015-08-22 18:05:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/InnoculateIT/?p=20', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(21, 1, '2015-08-20 16:38:15', '2015-08-20 16:38:15', '<div class="field field-name-field-description field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">\r\n<div class="field-items">\r\n<div class="field-item even">\r\n\r\nWith the release of Java 8 and planning already underway for Java 9+, the entire 9M+ Java community is energized in learning more about the latest additions to the Java platform and ecosystem. This track will cover new Java features such as Lambdas, Streams, New Concurrency primitives, new JVM languages and explore how to optimize performance in Java-based systems. We''ll also investigate how enterprises are exploring the use of Java Embedded in an Internet of Things world.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="field field-name-field-video field-type-file field-label-hidden">\r\n<div class="field-items">\r\n<div class="field-item even">\r\n<div class="media-youtube-video media-youtube-1"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Java Innovations - The Latest Trends in Java Technology', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-20 16:38:15', '2015-08-20 16:38:15', '', 20, 'http://localhost/InnoculateIT/index.php/2015/08/20/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
